\Scontrol column tab mode.
When on, the TAB key advances to the next column of 8 spaces.
When off, the TAB key advances to the next word in the line above.
\Scontrol overwrite mode.
When on, typed characters replace existing text.
When off, typed characters are inserted into existing text.
\Scontrol wordwrap mode.
When on, line breaks are inserted to break up typed characters into a paragraph.
When off, you must insert line breaks yourself.
